---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Links AI" description="Links AI helps service businesses turn recurring operational work into practical AI systems that reduce manual work and improve response time." pageClass="page-home">
  <section class="hero" slot="hero">
    <h1>AI systems for the work your business deals with every day.</h1>
    <p>
      We help service businesses improve recurring operational work like intake,
      follow-up, routing, and reporting without forcing a full overhaul.
    </p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What Links AI actually does</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>We find the right workflow to fix first</h3>
        <p>We look for repetitive work that slows the business down, creates admin drag, or causes inconsistent follow-up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>We build around how your team already works</h3>
        <p>We use your real tools, your real process, and your real constraints so the system fits the business instead of fighting it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>We launch something useful</h3>
        <p>Our goal is practical improvement: less manual work, faster response times, cleaner handoffs, and better visibility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>We keep improving it after launch</h3>
        <p>Once the first workflow is working, we refine it, support it, and expand into adjacent workflows when it makes sense.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Good first use cases</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Operations and admin</h3>
        <p>Intake, routing, status updates, recurring follow-up, and reporting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Customer and tenant communication</h3>
        <p>Common questions, message triage, response support, and handoff to the right person.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Sales follow-up</h3>
        <p>Lead response, outbound support, reminders, qualification, and pipeline hygiene.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Documents and internal workflows</h3>
        <p>Classification, summaries, workflow triggers, and cleanup of repetitive internal tasks.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Start simple</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>See how we work</h3>
        <p>Get the clear version of what working with Links AI looks like from first conversation through launch and improvement.</p>
        <p><a href="/how-it-works">View how it works →</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Read our thinking</h3>
        <p>Browse practical writing on AI operations, workflow design, and where small and mid-size businesses should start.</p>
        <p><a href="/insights">Read insights →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-box">
    <h2>Start with one workflow that is worth fixing</h2>
    <p>Tell us where the manual work piles up. We will help you figure out the best next move.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Request a call</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
